  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A divine entity helps ensure you can continue the fight. You have a pool of four d12s that you can spend to heal yourself. As a Bonus Action, you can expend dice from the pool, roll them, and regain a number of Hit Points equal to the roll's total.</p><p>Your pool regains all expended dice when you finish a Long Rest.</p><p>The pool's maximum number of dice increases by one when you reach Barbarian levels 6 (5 dice), 12 (6 dice), and 17 (7 dice).</p><section id=\"secret-JPShemp5GgsbDUiX\" class=\"secret\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The pool's increase is automatically handled in this feature. This feature also allows scaling up the number of dice you would like to expend for healing.</p></section>",
